data.text:
Engaged to boyfriend Brian Presley on April 19, 2002. He proposed to her in front of the Sleeping Beauty Castle at Disneyland in California.

Gave birth to her 1st child at age 30, a son Jackson Gunnar Presley on January 7, 2007. Child's father is her husband, Brian Presley.

Gave birth to her 2nd child, a daughter Emma Presley, with her husband Brian Presley. (2010)

Gave birth to her 3rd child at age 36, a daughter Ruby Rose Presley in June 2013. Child's father is her husband, Brian Presley.
